title: Cossacks Back To War ITALiAN Repack
description:
Cossacks - Back to war is an expansion of the famous game Cossacks
It's Standalone, you won't need the normal game
Cossacks I is one of the most important strategic Videogame of XXI century

The game modes do not present key innovations compared to previous versions of the game and take place in succession after finishing basic training. There are also 10 highly replayable missions but without the possibility to change the start options . In the main menu you can use a Level editor of maps and scenarios , which are then only used for playing in a group with modem on the LAN or on the Internet .

It Add some nation to the base-game

Enjoy :)
